================
description
================

1) This program accept file name from user and print all information about that file.
2) Required filename will be taken from command line

================
about the code
================

	input	:	file name
	output	:	result - information about file
 			
=============
How to run
=============

	make	:	compile the code and generates executable file as "myexe"
	make run:	run the executable with command line argument
			for this you have to pass parameter as: 
			
			$ make run p="parameter_value"
	
=============
NOTE
=============

	1)If the given file is unable to open (or unable to get information about file) then it will 
	display the appropriate reason of failure.
	2)This program implements "$ stat <file_name>" command.
	
